'''Haruspexes''' were [[Fortune teller/Legends|fortune-telling]] entrail-readers from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Darlyn Boda/Legends|Darlyn Boda]]. If and when a person presented a haruspex with a freshly killed [[toccat]], the haruspex would give a specific, accurate prophecy regarding the person.

==Behind the scenes==
Haruspicy, the inspection of the entrails of sacrificed animals, was a practice that began before the rise of the [[Wikipedia:Etruscan civilization|Etruscan]] and [[Wikipedia:Ancient Rome|Roman]] [[Wikipedia:civilization|civilizations]]. Whereas the plural of "haruspex" in real life is "haruspices," the ''[[Star Wars]]'' universe changes it to "haruspexes."

